What an amazing view, I feel bless to live in a country where I can explore the great outdoors and exercise my many freedoms! Unfortunately many members of our military have had to endure great hardships to secure those freedoms, and some have made the ultimate sacrifice... Luckily, they and their families are not forgotten!
.
I recently had an opportunity to learn about @dogtagbrewing, a veteran-owned and operated company that makes beer with a twist: 100% of their profits are donated to supporting America's Gold Star Families and legacy-building projects for their lost loved ones. Yes, 100%. Each can proudly remembers and is dedicated to a different soldier though a visual representation of their dog tags on the outside. Dog Tag Brewing Foundation then uses the sales of their beer to provide financial grants and free consulting to families to help establish and fund 501(c)(3) legacy projects to honor these Fallen Warriors.
.
If you get a chance, please check out their IG/FB/website for more in-depth information. Hopefully you'll give one (or a few!) a try as well. 🍺🇺🇸 #toastahero #neverforget #usmilitary #lovemycountry #merica #dogtagpartner
